The issue concentrates on tackling the difficulties brought about by the vast quantity of information that is available in the
modern world, along with the challenge of recognizing and understanding the most important parts of it.
The objective is to provide an interactive platform with sophisticated language processing that is easily comprehended byusers.
As a result, we came up with the concept to develop a platform that would summarize the content.
In general, the articles are too long for us to read in a short amount of time.
We have an idea to developed a platform named ASP for to summarize the articles.
This platform summarization the article in a small paragraph by using html and bootstrap languages.
